WEBVTT

00:02:28.585 --> 00:02:31.013
But many times they also
talked about health.

00:02:33.171 --> 00:02:35.949
The conversations about health
were lengthy and deep.

00:02:37.395 --> 00:02:40.584
The men often recounted
their doctor's recommendations

00:02:40.608 --> 00:02:42.699
to cut salt in their diet

00:02:42.723 --> 00:02:45.444
or to eat less fried foods

00:02:45.468 --> 00:02:47.689
or to stop smoking

00:02:47.713 --> 00:02:49.222
or to reduce stress.

00:02:49.911 --> 00:02:53.332
They talked about the different ways
you could reduce stress,

00:02:53.356 --> 00:02:55.611
like simplifying one's love life --

00:02:56.378 --> 00:03:00.842
(Laughter)